# fold-sub-constants

## Description

Constant folding via a computed-RHS applier (RFC 0090 Phase 2 applier
vocabulary). The replacement value is computed from the matched constants.

## Rewrite

lhs: (sub (const-int ?a) (const-int ?b))
apply: fold_sub("?a", "?b")
